​
Let us help host your next team outing,
c

m building event
!
PRIVATE & SEMI-PRIVATE OPTIONS
​
​
​
​
​
​
​
​
​
SAN MARCO
​
for groups of 20 to 60 people
​
Semi-private events can be booked for groups of 20 to 60 guests.  Group sizes over 60 people will require a full venue rental (please inquire for pricing).  Groups sizes of 20-60 have a semi-private 2-3 bay option + patio.
​
​
​
BOOK NOW - SAN MARCO
​
GATE PARKWAY
for groups of 20 to 250 people
​
Private events can be booked for groups of 20 to 250 guests.  Group sizes over 80 people will require a full venue rental (please inquire for pricing).  Groups sizes of 20-80 have a private 1to 4 bay option with one oversized VIP simulator bay, in addition to its own private restroom and hang out space.
​
​
​
​
​
*Please note that a group size of less than 20 will not require a private event.  If you are looking to book two bays side by side (to accommodate a total group of 16), please book through our online booking page and find a time where Bays with consecutive numbers are available simultaneously. We cannot guarantee exact bay placement until the day of your reservation unless a private event is booked. Note Gate Parkway Bays 1 & 6 and San Marco Bays 1 & 2 are not adjacent to any other bays.
BOOK NOW - GATE
